	<td>
		<p>
			<font face="verdana" size="3" color="#9f3215"><b>    Shestar's Half Finished Coif</b></font>
			<br>
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="#9f3215">
			<b><a href="mailto:">Baktosh <Tarrew Marr></a> | 
                        04/28/2000 3:52:03 PM</b></font></p>
			
			<p>
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">Talk to Trooper Shestar near the Field of Bone entrance. He will tell you that if you bring him 3 loose scales from scaled wolves, and 5gp, he will give you the Shestar Coif. Unfortunately, when you do, he states it is unfinished and that he is too busy to complete it. You need to gather 3 more wolf scales, i believe the green ones, and take them to a forge to combine yourself. Blacksmithing is required, as to how high I am not sure. I have tried this twice now, and lost everything. The GM's think it might be bugged, and are looking into it....
	<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
			</p>
	</td>
		<td>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
		
