				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Here's what I have found.<BR>
3 scales (the rarer green ones that don't stack) and the unfinished coif do not combine.<BR>
3 scales, the unfinished coif and a flask of bloodwater do not combine.<BR>
3 scales, the unfinished coif and a flask of water do not combine.<BR>
Here is where I ran out of wolf scales.<BR>
I suggest trying 2 flasks of water with the scales and coif.<BR>
Also, 3 loose scales and all those above do not combine either, just to be safe.  <BR>
Diomedes of The Rathe
