			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ok, I noticed the guy above say that he tried green scales, but the ones that work are the RED scales found on Scaled Wolves in the Scorpion Pit in FOB.  I gave him 3 red scales and 5 GP and he gave me the Unfinished Coif.  Now, either you are supposed to: 1. use the Unfinished Coif and 3 more red scales in the forge  OR  2. Combine the Unfinished Coif, 3 red scales, and water in the forge.  At level 11, I'm still not very good at blacksmithing to do this and the instructions aren't clear whether to add water or not to make the coif.  He just says that he hopes you are a good blacksmith and sends you on your way.<BR>
<BR>
Personally, I think this is Verant's way of forcing people to increase their skills in order to complete quests.  Most items are No Drop so you can't have someone else do it.
				</font>
